{"tid":120843,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個麒麟怪經歷","createTime":"2017-02-14T17:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T03:26:20.000Z","uid":18521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e01e14d3b70cadb4f0a000f800801da882e73233","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"時間點：8月，2015<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟住村屋，村口就有個涼亭嘅，我返屋企就要經過個涼亭入條村到。<br />\n<br />\n個排sem break收工返到條村都接近淩晨1點，聽同睇到涼亭有對父母係到教個仔數學，都奇怪緊，咁岩我行過個陣，佢地就問個仔7*9=幾多，個仔冇出聲，個呀媽就話：「咁都唔識嘅，哥哥仔，你知唔知呀？」，咁我就另轉頭答「63囉？」（個陣已經過左個亭入緊條村），跟著就走左。<br />\n<br />\n其實我個刻好想戴眼鏡望清楚佢地個樣，但係無啦啦戴又好怪，只係隱約見到3個人。<br />\n<br />\n又有次係屋企，個陣係黃大仙住，咁有晚星期六我就自己係屋企，熄完電視就訓，第朝竟然比個電視聲嘈醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 雖然覺得好撚怪，但都係照開電腦打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：部電視壞壞地，有時熄完會開返，但多數都係即刻開返，唔會咁耐，由其是到我訓著個刻都係未聽到電視聲。"},{"pid":"607dfb24d1b4075f9dc6766580336676ec468b50","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"全部屬實，認真冇吹水亦唔係講故"},{"pid":"bba98472e5d9ef6f3be95375aad9752ea0b09517","tid":120843,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a1dff3df659554ba4f5a32c4d8ec186c86d9b0","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有病睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，咁真係發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8aa39f22513a8eff683f51133d87b0362f0dbc5","tid":120843,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"撞野"},{"pid":"a00800080575393f27aea89e42601a554da8852c","tid":120843,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb5abc53ea23d8cd55ed1bd18ce7d8d6af3a845","tid":120843,"uid":27831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"我都試過幾次電視突然間開咗<br />\n之後繼續打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a35fdf979f148a71c62c4e3a7013ba4a9e0922","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞野</blockquote><br />\n其實我一路行一路全副心機諗佢地<br />\n<br />\n因為其實佢地講野同教仔個氣氛幾和諧幾溫馨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00082c9a91eebc906fb3d9f524fe9874aeb13c7","tid":120843,"uid":75032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:11:05.000Z","msg":"串緊佢個仔，連路人甲都識啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6beb80fd102bad3cb184d5a005cf7a153c59e290","tid":120843,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:23:45.000Z","msg":"前幾年有晚打緊機，嗰晚都幾凍吓嘅<br />\n咁我著哂一路打到凌晨一點，然後個妹出咗房去廁所，去完又返房<br />\n喺佢返房嗰時，盞燈熄咗<br />\n由於佢平時好鐘意熄我燈，所以我以為係佢做<br />\n咁我開返燈又繼續打機<br />\n我一路打一路諗，覺得好唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我望到燈掣位，佢要熄燈又要經過我身後，冇理由又見唔到人又熄到我燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後打打吓愈嚟愈凍<br />\n我淆底，所以即刻熄機瞓"},{"pid":"ab9c1eae4e65d93cbeb42b3b501f653cf36cfbba","tid":120843,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T23:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50fa76a6c3fb3dae90d4b3c99bf0bcff525859e","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>串緊佢個仔，連路人甲都識啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係奇怪在個時間點<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解要係個亭教唔係屋企教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然暑假姐，個仔唔洗訓咩"},{"pid":"8468af2038d7c7efbcba41ff37a9df623af25425","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾年有晚打緊機，嗰晚都幾凍吓嘅<br />\n咁我著哂一路打到凌晨一點，然後個妹出咗房去廁所，去完又返房<br />\n喺佢返房嗰時，盞燈熄咗<br />\n由於佢平時好鐘意熄我燈，所以我以為係佢做<br />\n咁我開返燈又繼續打機<br />\n我一路打一路諗，覺得好唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我望到燈掣位，佢要熄燈又要經過我身後，冇理由又見唔到人又熄到我燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後打打吓愈嚟愈凍<br />\n我淆底，所以即刻熄機瞓</blockquote><br />\n姐係你個燈掣離佢間房遠嘅？"},{"pid":"a13a62ebe9f52a48c0105167c4627609c4f1d960","tid":120843,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前幾年有晚打緊機，嗰晚都幾凍吓嘅<br />\n咁我著哂一路打到凌晨一點，然後個妹出咗房去廁所，去完又返房<br />\n喺佢返房嗰時，盞燈熄咗<br />\n由於佢平時好鐘意熄我燈，所以我以為係佢做<br />\n咁我開返燈又繼續打機<br />\n我一路打一路諗，覺得好唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我望到燈掣位，佢要熄燈又要經過我身後，冇理由又見唔到人又熄到我燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後打打吓愈嚟愈凍<br />\n我淆底，所以即刻熄機瞓</blockquote><br />\n姐係你個燈掣離佢間房遠嘅？</blockquote><br />\n好遠吓，應該唔可能喺我見唔到嘅情況下衝去熄燈再衝返入房"},{"pid":"c8d744556d4fa44d765b14ef4f81153c19568b46","tid":120843,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前幾年有晚打緊機，嗰晚都幾凍吓嘅<br />\n咁我著哂一路打到凌晨一點，然後個妹出咗房去廁所，去完又返房<br />\n喺佢返房嗰時，盞燈熄咗<br />\n由於佢平時好鐘意熄我燈，所以我以為係佢做<br />\n咁我開返燈又繼續打機<br />\n我一路打一路諗，覺得好唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我望到燈掣位，佢要熄燈又要經過我身後，冇理由又見唔到人又熄到我燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後打打吓愈嚟愈凍<br />\n我淆底，所以即刻熄機瞓</blockquote><br />\n姐係你個燈掣離佢間房遠嘅？</blockquote><br />\n好遠吓，應該唔可能喺我見唔到嘅情況下衝去熄燈再衝返入房</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f0828cff1a62de8c500422b14e06a8c1ded9fc","tid":120843,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"有幾撚怪啊？"},{"pid":"58ed78f8a8923772a98b2be223f06a0436786265","tid":120843,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前幾年有晚打緊機，嗰晚都幾凍吓嘅<br />\n咁我著哂一路打到凌晨一點，然後個妹出咗房去廁所，去完又返房<br />\n喺佢返房嗰時，盞燈熄咗<br />\n由於佢平時好鐘意熄我燈，所以我以為係佢做<br />\n咁我開返燈又繼續打機<br />\n我一路打一路諗，覺得好唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我望到燈掣位，佢要熄燈又要經過我身後，冇理由又見唔到人又熄到我燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後打打吓愈嚟愈凍<br />\n我淆底，所以即刻熄機瞓</blockquote><br />\n姐係你個燈掣離佢間房遠嘅？</blockquote><br />\n好遠吓，應該唔可能喺我見唔到嘅情況下衝去熄燈再衝返入房</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能係習慣問題，我有時沖涼果陣，我呀哥入黎去廁所之後出返去都會幫我關左燈，之後我就會大聲屌出黎，佢先話：呀！唔記得左"}]}